; position: relative; width: 2px; height: 20px; top: 6px;"><img src="//disney.go.com/globalmedia/chrome/images/divide.png" border="0" width="2" height="20"></span></td><td style="padding: 0px; height: 25px;" height="25"><div style="padding: 0px; position: relative; height: 12px; z-index: 150; top: 8px;"><a href="http://transfer.go.com/cgi/transfer.dll?srvc=dis&amp;goto=http://home.disney.go.com/liveevents/index&amp;name=g_micChrome_cl_Live%20Events" class="chromeLink" id="chromeLinkLiveEvents" target="_top" name="&amp;lid=chrome_micro_live+events&amp;lpos=chrome_micro"><span style="padding: 0px; font: bold 10px Arial; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0px;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Live Events</kw></span></a></div><div style="padding: 0px; position: relative; height: 12px; z-index: 140; top: -3px; left: 1px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;"><span style="padding: 0px; font: bold 10px Arial; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0px;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Live Events</kw></span></div></td><td style="padding: 0px 5px; height: 12px; vertical-align: top;" height="25"><span style="padding: 0px; position: relative; width: 2px; height: 20px; top: 6px;"><img src="//disney.go.com/globalmedia/chrome/images/divide.png" border="0" width="2" height="20"></span></td><td style="padding: 0px; height: 25px;" height="25"><div style="padding: 0px; position: relative; height: 12px; z-index: 150; top: 8px;"><a href="http://transfer.go.com/cgi/transfer.dll?srvc=dis&amp;goto=http://home.disney.go.com/travel/index&amp;name=g_micChrome_cl_Travel" class="chromeLink" id="chromeLinkTravel" target="_top" name="&amp;lid=chrome_micro_travel&amp;lpos=chrome_micro"><span style="padding: 0px; font: bold 10px Arial; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0px;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Travel</kw></span></a></div><div style="padding: 0px; position: relative; height: 12px; z-index: 140; top: -3px; left: 1px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;"><span style="